---
title: Creamy Mushroom & Bacon Linguine with Rocket & Tomato Salad
description: This linguine dish pairs the earthy flavour of mushroom and rosemary with an easy creamy bacon sauce. The side salad balances the
richness of the pasta with peppery rocket and fresh tomato.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-mushroom-rosemary-fettuccine-0bce935e.jpg
